Obba Babatundé https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Obba_Babatund%C3%A9 0 Obba Babatundé (born December 1, 1951) is an American stage and movie actor. A native of Queens, New York, Babatundé has appeared in more than seventeen stage productions, thirty theatrical films, sixty made-for-television movies, and two prime-time series.
